metadata.description:
###The NFT Yearbook Example - See what it will be like to interact with the NFT Yearbook. Best viewed and interacted with on **Opensea**
  Whether you manipulate the book with your mouse, use the buttons to open or close it, zoom in or out, or move around with the control buttons, ** The NFT Yearbook ** gives you an unprecedented amount of control to view every inch of your Book from every angle!
  ###Controls:
  ####1.Desktop/Laptop
 -Control + Mouse: Moves Book around
 -Mouse: Rotate Book 
  -Scroll or Right Click & Move: Zoom In or Out 
  -Book Button: Open or Close Book
  ####2.Smartphone
  -2 Fingers: Moves Book Around 
  -1 Finger: Rotates Book 
  -2 Finger Pinch: Zoom 
  -Book Button: Open or Close Book
   Visit [our website](https://nftyearbook.io/) for more information about ** The NFT Yearbook **.
